quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,12,"Hino woodani on onon resu…ďe, feccere e ko rew…ďe mon acci, si tawii …ďe jogaaki …ďi…ó…óo woni gorko maa debbo, woni ko onon …ďe jibinani maa gorko goo Si tawii hi…ďe jogii …ďi…ó…óo woni gorko maa debbo, hino woodani on naya…ďal e kon ko …ďa acci e jawdi ; ko yo on senndane …óum …ďaawo nde wasiyee ma…ď…ďe on siineede √Īamaale ma…ď…ďe …óen yo…ďitee. Hino woodani kadi resaa…ďe mon …ďen, naya…ďal e ko accu…óon kon, si tawii on jogaaki …ďi…ó…óo -woni gorko maa debbo, woni …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa …ďi…ó…ďe gorko goo. Si tawii hi…óon jogii …ďi…ó…óo -woni gorko maa debbo, hino woodani …ďe jeetata…ďal e ko accu…óon kon ; …ďe senndaŇčte …óum …ďaawo nde wasiyee mon on siineede √Īamaale mon …óen yo…ďitee. Si gorko maayii o jogitaaki maw…ďe maa …ďi…ó…óo, maa debbo si maayii o jogitaaki maw…ďe maa …ďi…ó…óo, kono hara on maay…óo hino jogitii neene-gooto gorko maa debbo ; hino woodani e …ďen neene-gootoo…ďe makko jeega…ďal farlaangal, si tawii non …ďen neene-gootoo…ďe makko wor…ďe maa rew…ďe hino …óuu…ói ; haray hino woodani …ďe denndaangal kafugol tata…ďal farlaangal, rew…ďe e wor…ďe ma…ď…ďe fotay e maggal, ko woni tun, …ďe henndike ge…ďal ma…ď…ďe ngal woo …ďaawo nde wasiyee maay…óo on siineede √Īamaale makko …óen yo…ďitee, e sarti hara on wasiyee wonaa lorroowo ronoo…ďe …ďen ; wano wasiyorgol ko …ďuri tata…ďal jawdi makko ndin. Ndee √Īaawoore nde wonnde e oo Aaya, ko Yamiroore nde Alla Wa…ó…óini e moo…óon. Alla ko Anndu…óo ko mo∆ī∆īani jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen aduna e laakara, Mu√Ī√Īii…óo Mo Hawjanaa lette yeddoo…ďe …ďen."
  4,13,"∆äen √Ďaawooje jaŇčtaa…óe fii wondu…ďe …ďen e wo…ó…ďe goo, ko Sari'aaji Alla …ói O Sar'ini e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen fii yo …ďe gollitir. Kala on …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, o gollitiri Yamirooje Makko …óen o wo…ó…óitii Ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, Alla Naadoyay mo Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata doga ley ku…ďeeji mun, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe nder majji poomaa. Ko ndin njo…ďdi Joomiiko woni maloore mawnde nde sugu mun alaa."
  4,14,"Kala on yeddu…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, o roŇčki huutorde √Ďaawooje Makko …óen maa o sikkitii …óe, o jaggiti Keeri Makko …óin, O Naadoyay mo yiite nge o √Īii…ďata e muu…óum ; e kadi no woodani mo ton lept hoynooje."